if the cops are around.

340
00:37:48,322 --> 00:37:50,722
Give it to me!
Hurry up, you bastard!

341
00:37:50,925 --> 00:37:54,019
Give me the money to get lost!
Don't shoot... don't...!

342
00:37:54,295 --> 00:38:00,200
You! Don't move! Don't mess around!
Oh shit!

343
00:38:03,938 --> 00:38:05,735
Got the money! Let's go!

344
00:38:08,242 --> 00:38:10,142
