up to sing in the nightclub.

368
00:42:33,708 --> 00:42:36,302
He told me I'd make a lot of money!

369
00:42:38,045 --> 00:42:40,843
At that time, I was only dreaming...

370
00:42:41,015 --> 00:42:43,609
The moment I arrived in Saigon,
he took my passport

371
