476
00:52:43,650 --> 00:52:44,947
Don't move!

477
00:52:45,252 --> 00:52:47,743
Sally, Sally!

478
00:52:51,591 --> 00:52:53,388
Will me make it?

479
00:52:54,795 --> 00:52:56,092
Let's go now.

480
00:52:58,065 --> 00:52:59,157
Watch out!

481
00:53:26,259 --> 00:53:28,659
