leave me out of it.

485
00:53:35,702 --> 00:53:36,896
Stop it, Paul!

486
00:53:37,003 --> 00:53:39,597
If we're still buddies.
It's not important.

487
00:53:39,806 --> 00:53:40,704
Let's get the hell out first!

488
00:53:40,874 --> 00:53:42,364
