499
00:54:32,559 --> 00:54:35,756
Sally, don't worry! Ben will help
you, even without your passport.

500
00:54:35,962 --> 00:54:39,659
We could be refugees,
sneak in Hong Kong.

501
00:55:00,687 --> 00:55:01,881
Sally!

502
00:55:08,195 --> 00:55:10,891
You see! I told you not to worry.

503
00:55:11,031 --> 00:55:12,828
We'll get back to Hong Kong, right!

504
00:55:13,934 --> 00:55:16,129
Hey! Release Mr. Leong!

505
00:55:32,152 --> 00:55:33,346
Take your clothes off.

506
00:55:37,190 --> 00:55:38,088
Boss!...

507
00:55:39,125 --> 00:55:41,116
Not Mr. Leong, he's our brother.

508
00:56:05,452 --> 00:56:06,350
Go to hell!

509
00:56:40,720 --> 00:56:41,914
Where's my passport?

510
00:56:45,292 --> 00:56:46,884
